    "methodology": "LSE covers approximately 1.6 million employees in private sector enterprises with 3+ employees. Figures are gross annual salary in CHF including 13th month where applicable. ISCO-08 occupation codes. P25/P50/P75 derived from published percentile tables. Updated to 2024 via BFS annual wage index for Switzerland (+2.9% cumulative CHF 2022-2024). BFS LSE every 4 years; next release expected 2026.",
